flexibleContent.content: We provide our clients with their very own team of expert security data scientists, engineers and analysts, to build perfectly tailored solutions.
flexibleContent.heading: Our experts handle everything you want them to.

flexibleContent.content: Our Experts build client-specific solutions that help organisations better identify, understand and respond to cyber Risk.
flexibleContent.heading: Experienced. Proven. Respected.

usps.content: We have unparalleled experience applying analytics to tackle some of the most complex cyber problems—for governments and the world’s largest enterprises.
usps.heading: Leverage our experience

usps.content: Expert data science talent combined with specialised security knowledge is hard to find and train. And building sophisticated security solutions requires that talent. We have those people available now.
usps.heading: Stop wasting time finding talent

usps.content: Building solutions from scratch is expensive. Accelerate your progress by leveraging our broad and deep library of analytics—then have our Experts tune them specifically to your needs.
usps.heading: Don’t squander investment

slides.heading: Hard to find talent must be recruited.
Data parsers must be built and data ingested.
Analytics and applications need to be built from scratch.

slides2.heading: No need to hire talent. Our team is ready to go.
No need to design and build a platform. Ours is pre-built and can be launched in hours.
Our data parsers are pre-built and can be deployed at lightning speed.
We have a range of out-of-the-box applications, models and visualisations that can be tailored with ease.
Mistakes won’t be made. Zero delays.
Business outcomes in weeks, then seen for many years.

flexibleContent.content: Our team of Security Analysts understands your requirements before defining your cyber problems.
flexibleContent.heading: Perfecting security Tradecraft.

noteContent.text: Our Experts have acquired their Tradecraft through deep experience in a security industry, and apply this skill to understanding your unique environment and the cyber Risks you face.

flexibleContent.content: Our team of Data Engineers is responsible for ingesting and transforming data—managing the  Platform with precision and insight.
flexibleContent.heading: Transforming Big Data into big value.

noteContent.text: Our Experts build data infrastructures, designing pipelines that transform disparate data into flexible, scalable data platforms.

flexibleContent.content: Our team of Security Data Scientists continuously build and extend analytics, contextualising data and creating powerful visualisations that provide complete clarity.
flexibleContent.heading: Pioneering Security Data Science.

noteContent.text: Our Security Data Scientists uniquely combine deep data science expertise with cyber domain knowledge to build analytics and applications that solve the toughest problems.

flexibleContent.heading: Our Expertise in action—Understand how our Expertise can be leveraged through this case study.

slides.content: A fast-growing security vendor and managed services provider.
slides.heading: The client

slides.content: The vendor came to Prevalent AI with a significant analytics development backlog and a desire to differentiate their solutions through the application of analytics. The vendor could not find data scientists due to lack of qualified talent and the prohibitive cost of resources. They also recognised that building and retaining a team (and developing analytics from scratch) would take too long and competitors would potentially move ahead.
slides.heading: The problem

slides.content: We  were able to provide a turn-key solution, with a team of dedicated security data science Experts, along with a range of pre-built analytics and related tools, that accelerated the development of new products while reducing cost.
slides.heading: The approach

slides.content: We ensured faster time to market and reduced overall costs.
slides.heading: The outcome

blocks.content: We leverage sophisticated technology to combine an almost unlimited range of data in one, central location. Rapid, scalable and highly cost effective.
blocks.heading: Our Platform

blocks.content: We bring out-of-the-box Analytics, ready to solve immediate challenges—then create tailored solutions to solve specific challenges (now and in the future).
blocks.heading: Our Analytics

footerCta.content: Our team of experts thrives when tackling complex cyber challenges. If you have one, we want to hear from you.
footerCta.heading: We seek the toughest cyber problems.

Managed Security and 3rd Party Risk Opportunity

cta.content: Learn how we’re helping global organisations take control of their cyber technology.
cta.heading: What we do

items.summary: A single, unified place for complex, disparate data.
A team of data scientists, engineers and analysts.
Learn more about the team behind Prevalent AI.
Whitepapers, blog articles, podcasts and more.
